(registered 2019-04-16, last updated 2019-04-16)

URI scheme name:
lorawan

Status:
provisional

Applications/protocols that use this URI scheme name:
This URI scheme has been defined in [1] for use with the Open Mobile Alliance LightweightM2M protocol over LoRaWAN networks. 

URI scheme syntax:
See section 6.7.4. "LoRaWAN Binding" in [1]. 

URI scheme semantics:
The "lorawan" URI indicates the FPort to send data to, from the Endpoint to the Application Server.

